TARGET

Usage: ^gTARGET [mount number] <mob/vehicle>^n

This command is used to target a mounted weapon at a target.
If you are rigging a vehicle you can select which mount to
target by putting the number refered to the mount in the
^WMOUNTS^n command in. Otherwise it will fire the gun you are
currently manning or all of them.

^WSee Also: MOUNT, MAN^n
